[SN]TITLE[SN]
The care home that's a nursery too

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Nurseries that are also care homes for the elderly are popular in countries like Japan and America.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
12 July 2017 Last updated at 16:07 BST
Now they are heading to England with the first to open very soon.
Studies show that having young children interacting with older people makes everyone feel a little happier.
Jenny has this report about a nursery in England which makes weekly visits to a home for the elderly.
